  "detailed_description": "<strong>Civilio is an open world multiplayer survival game. </strong><br>Here, your goal is to survive in an enviroment that is so hostile that even the chickens are murderous.<br>You must build up your base and make defenses to protect yourself from the mysterious enemies who do NOT like you, your presence and whatever teamwork you have built up with your pals.<br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2></u></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fully Multiplayer</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c3088adc8c59a2a15e9a3126fee31dee.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c3088adc8c59a2a15e9a3126fee31dee.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c3088adc8c59a2a15e9a3126fee31dee.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can enjoy this game with your friends<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight enemies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c685e242ac3436e530081633dcbb6221.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c685e242ac3436e530081633dcbb6221.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c685e242ac3436e530081633dcbb6221.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight the mysterious faction of raiders that want to destroy you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamemodes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/2e3f7aa117fac80982d00d40b36afe63.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/2e3f7aa117fac80982d00d40b36afe63.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/2e3f7aa117fac80982d00d40b36afe63.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can play in <strong>Survival</strong> if you seek a challening experience, or you can try the <strong>Creative</strong> gamemode where you are free of your mortal restrictions and can build anything you want.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skin customisation</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/e54c0b746c103e0c4fa64b656e19d838.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/e54c0b746c103e0c4fa64b656e19d838.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/e54c0b746c103e0c4fa64b656e19d838.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You have a plethora of possible skin combinations to choose from!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Persistent game state</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/9efdbdbf51096f654f7165747b1a57de.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/9efdbdbf51096f654f7165747b1a57de.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/9efdbdbf51096f654f7165747b1a57de.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Don't worry, all of your belongings will be saved on the host's computer!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Civilio is an open world multiplayer survival game. </strong><br>Here, your goal is to survive in an enviroment that is so hostile that even the chickens are murderous.<br>You must build up your base and make defenses to protect yourself from the mysterious enemies who do NOT like you, your presence and whatever teamwork you have built up with your pals.<br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2></u></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fully Multiplayer</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c3088adc8c59a2a15e9a3126fee31dee.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c3088adc8c59a2a15e9a3126fee31dee.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c3088adc8c59a2a15e9a3126fee31dee.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can enjoy this game with your friends<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight enemies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c685e242ac3436e530081633dcbb6221.poster.avif?t=1727988790\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c685e242ac3436e530081633dcbb6221.webm?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839230/extras/c685e242ac3436e530081633dcbb6221.mp4?t=1727988790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight the mysterious faction of raiders that want to destroy you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamemodes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop plays